am i a bad mom i love my son more than anything but something happened today that made me question my parenting my son is and we were at his friends house my son his friend also and his friends sister were all swimming the water came up to about my sons collarbone level but he seemed confident in the water so i let him go without any flotation device well about minutes into the swim i look over and my son is underwater trying to swim to the top he couldve stood up but i guess didnt realize it i screamed at the sister in the water to get him up but he was in the middle of the pool so i couldnt reach him i just kept yelling until she finally picked him up about seconds my son was fine i nearly had a heart attack and from then on made him wear the arm floaties but why didnt i jump in i wouldve and i briefly contemplated it but i was on the other side of the pool as the ladder and didnt know if i could make it in am i a bad mom this happened to me with my oldest four years ago when my oldest son was my son was in the bay right near the dock with my neighbor who was then the water was up to my son's waist he stepped on a rock and starting screaming and holding his foot and he went under the water if he stood up or started swimming he'd be fine but he was freaking out thinking he stepped on a jellyfish as we later found out i stood there watching my son from the dock about ft away screaming at my neighbor to grab him he didn't hear me at first and then turned around saw my son and grabbed him a good seconds later that day all i did was question myself why didn't i jump in you were in shock just as i was seeing your kid under the water and panicing because you're not standing right next to him to help him the millasecond you saw something happen to you sent you into fear you're not a bad mother in anyway you didn't scream at your son for going into water too deep you didn't let him stay under the water and hope he'd figure out what to do you were just nervous scared and in shock all in the same time if anything that shows how wonderful of a mom you are best wishes and heres to safe swimming Shaggy dog story Tag Episodes of Lost (Season 1) Aerial (dance move) Futurama (TV series - season 5) The Inside Diving Milton H. Erickson Futurama (TV series - season 2) StarCraft: Uprising The Grim Adventures of Billy and Mandy Swimming Pok__mon Live! Professional wrestling throws Jon Secada Piccolo Junior Saga Similarities between the Bible and the Qur'an Scream (film) The Curse of Fenric Columbine High School massacre The Fairly OddParents EastEnders Prank flash Suplex Pitaten Personal flotation device Swingout Volleyball Rent (musical) Vegeta Xiaolin Showdown Professional wrestling holds Episodes of Lost (Season 2) Breaststroke One Piece minor characters Ecco the Dolphin Avenue Q Recurring South Park characters Backstroke RuneScape quests The Ashlee Simpson Show Ben Johnson (athlete) Kimi Finster Miss Saigon Trapped in the Closet War of the Worlds (2005 film) Humphrey Bogart K' Darth Vader God Emperor of Dune The SpongeBob SquarePants Movie Tupac Shakur The Time Machine The Lion, the Witch and the Wardrobe Pakistani cricket team in West Indies in 2005 The dozens Charmed The Dalek Invasion of Earth Rose (Doctor Who) Piccolo (Dragon Ball) Full Metal Panic? Fumoffu PANICS Eric Cartman Chapterhouse Dune Kodocha Wheel of Fortune Operation Market Garden Calvin and Hobbes Ron and Fez Sin City Jam (TV series) The Arsenal of Freedom (TNG episode) About a Boy Mario series enemies Mount Everest Shark Blood (computer game) Apollo 11 Skateboarding trick Air Florida Flight 90 Saved by the Bell The Shining (film) One Tree Hill (TV series) Sharon Tate King Piccolo Saga Mercury 4 My Life as a Teenage Robot The Venture Bros. Father's Day (Doctor Who) Water polo Phoebe Halliwell Coming of Age (TNG episode) Haven (TNG episode) 